Possible data directory layout:

data/ 
	pilot_samples.hdf5              [hdf5 file from step 1]

[   method      targetcost      random trials  ]

    acvkl/
                tc100/
                    sample_allocation.hdf5      [saved by MXMC SampleAllocation]
                    input_outputs_trial1.hdf5
                        model0/                 [group]
                            *inputs_model1      [dataset]
                            *outputs_model1     [dataset]
                        ...
                        modelM/                 [group]

                    input_outputs_trial2.hdf5
                    ...
    
                tc500/
    ...
    mlmc/


Note: Instead of "model0", "model1" , etc. as names of groups in HDF5 files, can use the same convention used for pilot samples (names equal to time steps - "0.1/" , ...)
